      "value": "<p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640331/RenderMan_Houdini_Fire.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433075047&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=482\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640331/RenderMan_Houdini_Fire.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433075047&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640371\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Houdini_Fire.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640331\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0f3ac703-ee28-4e7f-a470-393ccd63df98\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640331/RenderMan_Houdini_Fire.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433075047&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1679&amp;height=900 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640331/RenderMan_Houdini_Fire.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433075047&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=482 1x\"></span></p><div class=\"section\"><p><br/>RenderMan for Houdini (RfH) is an integrated interface to RenderMan inside Houdini. </p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"46e8fc3e-c330-41bd-b7c5-98562ce6d509\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><p class=\"title\">Installation</p><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p><span>RenderMan for Houdini requires the installation of RenderMan Pro Server as well as the RfH plugin in order to function correctly. The RenderMan installer does this automatically.</span></p></div></div><p><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\"><br/>To complete the setup you should follow the directions for </span><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://www.sidefx.com/docs/houdini/basics/config_env\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\">I</a><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544640398/Installation+of+RenderMan+for+Houdini\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640398\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">nstallation of RenderMan for Houdini</a><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.0px;\">.</span></p></div>"
